    <mxCell id="secq_text" value="&lt;b style='font-size:13px;color:#FFFFFF;'&gt;Security (word Questionnaire)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:10px;color:#FFFFFF;'&gt;By completing the security information in the Infrastructure Blueprint, you're setting your application up for success.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Uncover and address potential vulnerabilities early, saving time and resources later.&lt;br&gt;• Clearly define data access and handling practices to simplify troubleshooting and scaling.&lt;br&gt;• Show stakeholders your commitment to protecting data and maintaining compliance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[Click on the Security Info Instructions Tab for Instructions and Examples]&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
